e target coordinate to fit within the viewport.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"targetCoordinate"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view. If ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the map fits the target instantaneously.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"animated"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This method has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"text":" property is set to a value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other than ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:ani